Welcome to the **Kali Linux Lab Manual** designed for students participating in the **RakshakPlus Cybersecurity Awareness Program**. This guide provides hands-on labs to build foundational ethical hacking and cybersecurity skills using Kali Linux in a safe, legal environment.

